 rhythm, shortness of breath, or syncope.', 'Metabolism', 'Pharmacologic response to tetrabenazine should be monitored more closely whenever a potent CYP450 2D6 inhibitor (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/78083/', '', 'Dalfampridine, Sodium oxybate, Riluzole, Inotersen, Amifampridine, Tafamidis', 'Imatinib, Dabrafenib, Acalabrutinib, Pexidartinib, Tepotinib, Avapritinib, Larotrectinib, Selumetinib, Cobimetinib, Capmatinib, Ibrutinib, More', 1767369485);
